OL,7,FShe has laid out the government's
OL,8,Fspending plans for the next three
OL,9,Fyears - showing us what the
OL,10,Fgovernment's priorities are and
OL,11,Fshaping the direction of travel until
OL,12,F2029.
OL,14,FThe chancellor told MPs: "We are
OL,15,Frenewing Britain. But I know that too
OL,16,Fmany people in too many parts of our
OL,17,Fcountry are yet to feel it.
OL,19,F"This government's task, my task as
OL,20,Fchancellor, and the purpose of this
OL,21,Fspending review, is to change that."
