OL,7,FWhat is the spending review and who
OL,8,Fare the biggest losers?
OL,10,FAlongside setting out her plans for
OL,11,Fdepartmental spending, the chancellor
OL,12,Fhas also outlined #113 billion of
OL,13,Finvestment in infrastructure and other
OL,14,Fcapital projects over the next four
OL,15,Fyears.
