OL,7,FBecause of the chancellor's "iron-
OL,8,Fclad" fiscal rules, she's got a
OL,9,Flimited amount of cash to play with
OL,10,Ffor day-to-day spending, and expected
OL,11,Fspending increases on health and
OL,12,Fdefence mean it's likely budgets in
OL,13,Fother areas will be squeezed.
OL,15,FBut last year Reeves also changed the
OL,16,Frules to allow her to borrow more
OL,17,Fmoney for investment in infrastructure
OL,18,F- that's why we've seen increased
OL,19,Fspending on big projects but some
OL,20,Fdepartmental budgets reduced.
