OL,7,FAmong the eight departments facing
OL,8,Freal-terms cuts over the next three
OL,9,Fyears are the Home Office (down 1.7% a
OL,10,Fyear), Foreign Office (down 6.9% a
OL,11,Fyear), Transport (down 5% a year),
OL,12,FEnvironment and Rural Affairs (down
OL,13,F2.7%), and Business and Trade (down
OL,14,F1.8% a year).
OL,16,FWhen pressed by ITV News Political
OL,17,FCorrespondent Carl Dinnen on the cuts,
OL,18,FReeves accepted "there are things that
OL,19,Fwe're not able to do, there are areas
OL,20,Fwhere there will be reductions in
OL,21,Fspending."
