OL,7,FBut the government also has a goal of
OL,8,Fhitting 3% of GDP on defence by the
OL,9,Fend of the next parliament, and it's
OL,10,Fexpected Nato countries will agree
OL,11,Flater this month to increasing defence
OL,12,Fspending further to 3.5%.
