OL,7,FThe chancellor spoke at length about
OL,8,Feducation during her speech, as she
OL,9,Fannounced day-to-day funding for
OL,10,Fschools will increase by #4.5 billion
OL,11,Fa year.
OL,13,F"I joined the Labour Party almost
OL,14,Fthirty years ago because I knew that
OL,15,Fthe Conservative government when I
OL,16,Fgrew up didn't care very much about
OL,17,Fschools like mine, or the kids I grew
OL,18,Fup with," she told MPs.
